column2: "Oh hey listen to this! I just saw something amazing here!"
"Earlier here there was a little girl surrounded by Darkers, I went to help her but..."
"All of a sudden she pulled out a rod and destroyed all of them with one technique!"
"I got hit too... But still she was on another level!"
"Since she was using photons, I thought she was in ARKS."
"Man, I really wish I could get closer to a girl like her..."
